                      block airblast reflects
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Example 1: not being able to push a stack of Stickybombs
                      with airblast
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Example 2: not being able to deflect an enemy projectile
                      due to a friendly Medic syringe in the way
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </li>
