                      The Scottish Resistance detonation ring is designed to
                      make trap detonation more consistent at all ranges
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      The Scottish Resistance now has an outer detonation ring
                      to help with trimming off bombs from traps
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Close distance bombs will no longer detonate if you are
                      not in the air (to make the stickyjumping check less
